comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T09:59:04.847Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"author=codex-sdk-wide-20260713,text=Duplicate check evidence: searched all tracker statuses for file/doc link management, dependency edge management, facet SDK files/docs/deps, and the full pm-usfg child lineage. pm-zwpp is the canonical parent; pm-a2h3 and earlier annotation work are closed, while no existing child owns the remaining S2 files/docs, S3 deps, and S4 direct-facade completion bundle. External baseline: open Dependabot PRs #537-#541; GitHub Dependabot, code-scanning, and secret-scanning alerts are empty; pnpm audit reports 0 vulnerabilities; Windows nightly failure is already tracked separately by pm-u5zr/pm-b24b; latest pm-changelog is 2026.7.12-2."
  "2026-07-13T09:59:20.214Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Implementation start: active bundle is pm-jcvg + pm-2ler only. Scope combines public files/docs/deps domain kernels, CLI-on-SDK presentation layering, dependency validation actionability, SDK docs/docstrings, exact coverage, packed temp-project proof, and full PR review/merge closeout. Parent pm-zwpp remains open as the canonical feature container rather than being marked in progress."
  "2026-07-13T10:11:41.839Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Implementation evidence: extracted linked-artifact, files, docs, and dependency command implementations into public SDK modules; kept CLI compatibility re-exports; routed PmClient/runtime directly through SDK primitives; added direct public exports, SDK documentation, and focused tests. Focused affected suite: 128/128 passed."
  "2026-07-13T10:35:48.048Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Final local evidence: release gates passed build, typecheck, docs/skills, strict static quality, package boundary, token budgets, exact coverage (279 files, 5,604 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines), version sync, secrets, packed npx smoke (12 packages), and 88-command package-first dogfood. Manual packed temp consumer /tmp/pm-sdk-manual-ujCqZK verified direct runFiles/runDocs/runDeps, PmClient readback, and active/historical/sentinel classification. Sentry/telemetry gate: critical=0, high=0 over 14 days; health warnings=0; history drift=0. Pre-commit release:gates stopped only at the Greptile review gate because review requires committed changes; it will be rerun on the PR head."
  "2026-07-13T10:45:29.820Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Greptile preflight review 79d26578-e567-4bfb-9aa6-9837c2c8eb3f: accepted both P2 findings. Preserved backward-compatible dangling_reference_count as active+terminal total while active_dangling_reference_count remains the warning/gating signal; documented the contract and updated assertions. Changed the collector test to import the public SDK module directly. Verification: focused deps+validate 97/97, strict static quality, package boundary, token budget, and docs/skills gates pass."
  "2026-07-13T11:13:04.126Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Hosted review round 1 implementation evidence: fixed files-discover apply race reporting so only newly committed links count as added/changed; bounded relative-path scanning to 32 KiB while retaining full absolute-path discovery; parallelized file probes; replaced resource-result double casts with a typed mapped result; and hardened dependency governance against malformed non-string runtime targets. Focused files/docs/deps suite passes 40/40 with typecheck."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-13T10:35:50.352Z",codex-sdk-wide-20260713,"Architecture learning: command-owned linked-resource kernels can move intact behind SDK modules while retaining thin CLI compatibility exports; the import-boundary ratchet then proves the migration by removing private CLI-to-core edges instead of adding exemptions."
